Chicago Mercantile Exchange floortraders and commission house representatives are guesstimatingtoday's hog slaughter at about 280,000 to 287,000 head versus257,000 week ago and 311,000 a year ago.    Saturday's hog slaughter is guesstimated at about 40,000 to55,000 head.    Cattle slaughter is guesstimated at about 121,000 to126,000 head versus 128,000 week ago and 136,000 a year ago.    Saturday's cattle slaughter is guesstimated at about 19,000to 35,000 head. Reuter&#3;